title: How long you can stay in extremely cold temperatures before getting frostbite
text:
11 PM EDT How long you can stay in extremely cold temperatures before getting frostbite 
Frostbite is a serious conditon. Cold temperatures can cause the skin and tissue to start freezing, killing the cells. But, wind-chill can drastically change how long you'll last.
